The most important changes:

*** common changes ***
* Add IPv6 support.
* Rewrite code from Boost to C++11 where it is possible.
* Improve Lua support.

*** eiskaltdcpp-qt ***
* Add Qt5 support.
* Add dialog widget for debugging Lua scripts.

*** eiskaltdcpp-gtk ***
* Get rid of deprecated Gtk+ 3.x elements.
* Confirugation dialog for IP filter.

